&lt;p&gt;Do you want to join a forward-thinking, friendly GP practice as a part-time doctor in a bustling city set in one of the most beautiful parts of England?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SSP Health has vacancies at our two practices in historic Carlisle – both rated ‘Good’ by the CQC.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SSP Health is a federation of practices so our GPs benefit from exceptional working conditions, which brings our doctors an enviable work/life balance, flexible hours and little very admin. As we have 37 practices across the North West, there are excellent opportunities to switch between surgeries, comprehensive in-house CPD support and many chances to progress your career and specialise. We are a licensed Tier 2 sponsor, so we welcome inquiries from outside the UK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On the doorstep of both the Lake District and Northumberland national parks, Carlisle is the economic capital of Cumbria and south-west Scotland. Enjoying a long history and with a rich cultural heritage, Carlisle is famous for having stunning countryside but also all the benefits of a modern, thriving university city. Directly on the M6 motorway, Carlisle is by train just over an hour to Glasgow and Edinburgh, just over two hours to Manchester Airport and three-and-a-half hours direct to London. People in the city enjoy a low cost of living with house prices well below the national average.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Our modern, efficient GP practices use the latest technology and processes and pride themselves on giving excellent healthcare to our patients. Come and join our team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NHS Pension available.&lt;/p&gt;
